txt.en: An impressive specimen of Orc, the Uruk Warleader commands and directs forces in battle.

Uruks use the Black Speech -- a guttural and perverse corruption of an ancient Elvish mode -- to form their names. Some common initial elements are Ak-, Bag-, Grish-, Lug-, Muz-, Shak-, and Shap-.\n\nSome common final elements are -bash, -burz, -dush, -gash, -luk, -nakh, and -rat.
